{"tid":440763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德政系列 沙田市中心錄15宗成交 好運中心443呎630萬同類新高","createTime":"2017-10-19T05:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T12:07:47.000Z","uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a647db593e09d29f55cd924df2473b9e4c18c3d0","tid":440763,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"沙田市中心錄15宗成交 好運中心443呎630萬同類新高<br />\n<br />\n2017年10月18日 17:21<br />\n<br />\n沙田市中心二手交投暢旺，美聯物業營業經理彭成昌指， 暫錄15宗成交，較上月同期上升五成。其中好運中心棕林閣高層D室，實用面積443平方呎，原則2房，望內園，剛以630萬易手，呎價14,221元，屬同類443平方呎單位的新高紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ps.hket.com/article/1927539/沙田市中心錄15宗成交\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1927539%2F%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E9%8C%8415%E5%AE%97%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4&d=lqIhu9U%2BCmjjKJE3AlZIxBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7f0d4fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ps.hket.com/article/1927539/沙田市中心錄15宗成交</a>"},{"pid":"7118fe672763b3d7874d30dd7449af4a7f49e88f","tid":440763,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:24:54.000Z","msg":"今日高位 明日低位<br />\n<br />\n應該要賣到800萬先算正常價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f76a216838f304338ac15977f0aa83b434228f0","tid":440763,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"好運都6百幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新城市未過800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba57f04927df4867a2ff29b6331ed10c10644cad","tid":440763,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited